csum=(:*toc-float:)Rice cookers are all the rage nowadays. They say you can't ever get a bad batch of rice if you use the rice cooker. But cooking rice is actually quite easy. This, like MakingPerfectPasta, is one of the signs that you've understood what it means to cook food. 
